WEBVTT

00:00.721 --> 00:02.255
My name is Elena Gilbert.

00:02.490 --> 00:05.571
I'm a new vampire, and there
have been complications.

00:05.671 --> 00:07.337
I know that I'm sired
to you, Damon.

00:07.339 --> 00:08.839
You know what would
make me happy?

00:08.841 --> 00:11.558
That what you actually felt for me
was real.

00:11.560 --> 00:13.360
But there's hope
now there's a cure.

00:13.362 --> 00:15.979
This cure has ruined us, and it
hasn't even been found yet.

00:15.981 --> 00:17.481
What do you know
about Silas?

00:17.483 --> 00:19.349
He's the world's first
immortal being,

00:19.351 --> 00:21.318
who just happens
to be the person with the cure.

00:21.320 --> 00:23.237
Unlikely alliances
have formed.

00:23.239 --> 00:24.321
What the hell
are you doing here?

00:24.323 --> 00:25.289
How can I help?

00:25.291 --> 00:28.525
No feelings.
No attachment.

00:31.329 --> 00:32.713
To make sure we
never find the cure.

00:32.715 --> 00:34.331
You're going to find
Jeremy Gilbert,

00:34.333 --> 00:35.999
and you're going to
kill him.

00:36.001 --> 00:37.835
Our only
chance is to risk everything.

00:37.837 --> 00:39.219
Kol compelled Damon
to kill you.

00:39.221 --> 00:41.505
You're gonna kill
Kol instead.

